{{lens_2_output}}

FILES TO READ IN FULL (from Pass 5, MUST_READ_FULLY list):
{{must_read_file_list}}

════════════════════════════════════════
YOUR OUTPUT FORMAT
════════════════════════════════════════
For EACH file in the must-read list, produce a complete annotation block.
Use this exact structure — do not skip any section, do not merge sections.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
